name: Collective Memories
description:
Our perspectives are shaped differently based on what we saw, heard and felt throughout many multi-sensory experiences in our life. But, sooner or later some lines, though sourced from many different backgrounds, will eventually converge. This convergence could be triggered even by the simplest of things. Turning what we once called, 'my memories' into a shareable network of topics which then became known as 'our memories'.

Maybe we can also call this phenomenon as 'Collective Memories'. A moment where all of us, as a collective, no matter how different our background is— can share our fondest memories together without boundaries, happily.

Artist: Jemala 
Title: Collective Memories 
Format: 44,1Khz 16bit Stereo WAV File 
Duration: 01:32
